title: IT'S A TRAP
description:
April 29th 1982, EMI - Elstree Studios, England.
A frustrated Richard Marquand is not getting the performance he needs
from one of his key actors, Timothy Rose. In a last ditch effort,
Marquand shows Rose, playing the role of Admiral Ackbar, a number of
films to help him prepare for his final scene of "Return of the
Jedi"...
